node_5.subject: Maria Lopez
node_5.description: This is Maria Lopez's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 8:00 am, read a generative agent paper from 8:30 am to 9:30 am, prepare the presentation based on the paper from 9:30 am to 9:45 am, give the presentation at 10:00 am, engage in conversations with Klaus Mueller and Isabella Rodriguez about the paper from 10:30 am to 11:00 am, continue reading and researching on generative agents and related topics from 11:00 am to 12:00 pm, have a lunch break and rest from 12:00 pm to 1:00 pm, resume reading and research from 1:00 pm to 4:00 pm.
